<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 12:24:34 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国滴滴出行第二季度扭亏为盈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-didi-global-swings-profit-second-quarter-2024-08-21/</link><description>中国最大的网约车公司滴滴出行第二季度净利润为人民币 14 亿元（合 1.9624 亿美元），而去年同期亏损人民币 3 亿元，该公司继续重建因监管打击而受到严重打击的业务。 。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 11:43:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-didi-global-swings-profit-second-quarter-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>由于产量和全球需求转温和，美国石油出口增长放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/us-oil-export-gains-slow-output-global-demand-turn-tepid-2024-08-21/</link><description>经过多年的强劲增长，美国原油出口增幅预计将在 2024 年趋于稳定，在全球石油需求依然低迷的情况下，国内产量预计将出现疫情以来的最低增幅。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 10:09:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/us-oil-export-gains-slow-output-global-demand-turn-tepid-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：无情的反弹暂停喘口气</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-08-21/</link><description>塞缪尔·因迪克 (Samuel Indyk) 展望美国和全球市场未来一天</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 10:07:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>美国检察官称，强制监禁是乔治桑托斯协议的关键</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/mandatory-prison-was-key-george-santos-deal-us-prosecutor-says-2024-08-21/</link><description>指控这位丑闻缠身的前美国国会议员的联邦检察官周二表示，乔治·桑托斯愿意在监狱中度过至少两年，这是他同意承认欺诈和身份盗窃罪的关键部分。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 10:03:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/mandatory-prison-was-key-george-santos-deal-us-prosecutor-says-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>小米第二季度营收超预期，公布汽车销量</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/xiaomi-q2-revenue-jumps-32-auto-business-smartphone-sales-2024-08-21/</link><description>中国小米公司周三公布的第二季度营收高于预期，首次披露其汽车业务部门的贡献为 62 亿元人民币（8.692 亿美元）。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 09:53:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/xiaomi-q2-revenue-jumps-32-auto-business-smartphone-sales-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国机构称欧盟电动汽车关税草案缺乏客观性、公平性</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-body-says-eu-draft-ev-tariffs-lacks-objectivity-fairness-2024-08-21/</link><description>中国一家行业机构周三表示，欧盟对中国电动汽车反补贴调查的调查结果草案缺乏客观性和公平性。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 09:36:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-body-says-eu-draft-ev-tariffs-lacks-objectivity-fairness-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>随着中国出货量的增加，印度4月至7月仍是钢铁净进口国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/india-remains-net-steel-importer-april-july-chinese-shipments-rise-2024-08-21/</link><description>路透社看到的临时政府数据显示，从四月份开始的本财年的前四个月，印度仍然是钢铁净进口国，中国是其最大的合金供应国。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 09:25:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/india-remains-net-steel-importer-april-july-chinese-shipments-rise-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国工商总局誓言在欧盟补贴调查结果草案后采取进一步措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-saic-vows-take-further-measures-after-eu-draft-findings-subsidies-2024-08-21/</link><description>中国上汽集团周三表示，在欧盟委员会公布对中国电动汽车反补贴调查结果草案后，上汽集团将采取进一步的法律措施保护自身权益。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 08:21:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-saic-vows-take-further-measures-after-eu-draft-findings-subsidies-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国对欧盟乳制品进口展开反补贴调查，以抵制电动汽车关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-opens-anti-subsidy-investigation-into-european-dairy-imports-2024-08-21/</link><description>周三，中国对从欧盟进口的乳制品启动了反补贴调查，在布鲁塞尔公布修改后的中国制造电动汽车关税计划的第二天，中国与欧盟的紧张关系加剧。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 07:38:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-opens-anti-subsidy-investigation-into-european-dairy-imports-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国表示对美国核战略报告“严重关切”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-says-it-is-seriously-concerned-about-us-nuclear-strategic-report-2024-08-21/</link><description>中国外交部周三表示，中国对有关美国批准核战略计划以打击中国核武库快速扩张的报道表示严重关切。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 07:27:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-says-it-is-seriously-concerned-about-us-nuclear-strategic-report-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国在推动文化发展的“黑神话：悟空”电子游戏上大肆宣传</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-goes-ape-over-culture-boosting-black-myth-wukong-video-game-2024-08-21/</link><description>中国官方媒体对中国迄今为止最成功的单人电子游戏表示支持，称其改编自明代史诗《西游记》将迫使西方玩家更多地了解中国的文化。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 06:10:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-goes-ape-over-culture-boosting-black-myth-wukong-video-game-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>港交所利润录得三个季度以来首次增长，IPO数量回升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kongs-bourse-reports-3-drop-first-half-profits-q2-activities-pick-up-2024-08-21/</link><description>随着新上市和交易活动的增加，香港交易所实现了三个季度以来的首次利润增长，创下了 4 月至 6 月期间的收入和收入纪录。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 04:35:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hong-kongs-bourse-reports-3-drop-first-half-profits-q2-activities-pick-up-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国汽车协会称欧盟对中国电动汽车征收关税草案带来“巨大风险”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-says-eu-draft-tariffs-chinese-evs-brings-enormous-risks-uncertainty-2024-08-21/</link><description>据中国国家广播电台中央电视台周三报道，中国汽车工业协会（CAAM）表示坚决反对欧盟针对中国制造的电动汽车征收惩罚性关税的修订草案。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 02:56:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-says-eu-draft-tariffs-chinese-evs-brings-enormous-risks-uncertainty-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>投资者期待美联储在股市复苏后采取下一步行动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1pix-2024-08-21/</link><description>全球股市在经历了长时间的反弹后，周三陷入了近期的高点，投资者等待周五美联储降息的线索，以决定下一步行动。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 02:17:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1pix-2024-08-21/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称正在调查被指控与中国犯罪有关的前市长越狱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-probing-escape-ex-mayor-accused-chinese-crime-links-2024-08-21/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯周三表示，菲律宾政府正在调查被指控与中国犯罪集团有联系的前市长郭爱丽如何设法逃离该国。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 01:55:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-probing-escape-ex-mayor-accused-chinese-crime-links-2024-08-21/</guid></item></channel></rss>